    public class EntityArmorInvWrapper
extends EntityEquipmentInvWrapper
    Exposes the armor inventory of an EntityLivingBase as an IItemHandler using EntityLivingBase.getItemStackFromSlot(net.minecraft.inventory.EntityEquipmentSlot) and EntityLivingBase.setItemStackToSlot(net.minecraft.inventory.EntityEquipmentSlot, net.minecraft.item.ItemStack).
